    This translation is released in public domain. It is a mere translation
  of original documentation of GuidePrefs by Bart Vanhaeren.
  This  guide file  (whose original name was `GuidePrefsI.guide', where `I'
  standt for `Italian')  should  be considered ź by Bart Vanhaeren, and may
  or may not :(, be included in furthers releases of GuidePrefs.
  Included  italian-catalog  (`locale/catalog/italiano/GuidePrefs.catalog')
  is ź by Bart Vanhaeren too.

  All the work was intented to support localization.
  @{B}If  you  are  capable  to  translate  catalogs  to  your language, please@{UB}
  @{B}consider the idea of translating catalogs:  this way people that does not@{UB}
  @{B}understand a single word of foreign  language may access several products@{UB}
  @{B}too. Let the Amiga comunity grow.@{UB}

